summary: The Potter Twins and the Philosopher's Stone
title: The Potter Twins and the Philosopher's Stone
body:
On that fateful Halloween night when James and Lily Potter are murdered, their infant twins, Harry and Aralynn, are sent to live in separate homes—Aralynn with a magical family, and Harry with an ordinary one. However, when they’re both accepted to Hogwarts, and things start to get spooky.

Revelation

The time for reconsideration was gone. Before, they could have chosen any moment to turn back. They could have decided they that they weren’t meant to stop the Philosopher’s Stone from being stolen…

Read more…

blog.name: pendantstyles
blog.title: you bring me home
blog.description:
hannah | vision isn’t 20/20, but harry is!!

+ requests are always open! +

masterlist

question: harry embracing the dadlife ™️
answer:
okay this fucking cracks me up and destroys me at the same time

harry would let it be his own life, 10/10.

he’d go out and get new clothes for the bub with the angel herself and the missus and he’s gonna be carrying and put little shades on her (gucci, what do you expect) and you best believe harry has a fucking fANNY PACK ON HIM. missus feels a bit dizzy? he has vick’s there, don’t worry. the patch he put on angel’s clothes is not enough for the mosquito he sees flying to her ten feet away? he has a whole pack of them in there, fyi. angel gets fussy and hungry for something else other than missus’ breast milk? harry has easily-digested biscuits that has a bit of sugar in it to keep her happy.

he sees a ‘daddy is my favorite’ and ‘daddy is cool’ and other twenty variations of it? he buys it instantly with no hesitation (but he isn’t that careless so he’ll pick it up first and deems it if it’s soft enough to be worn by baby angel, looks at the tag to double-check but never the price, he’s too cool for that).

he sees little breathable variations of suits he has? DOUBLE-FUCKING WIN! he’d buy them in no time and dress her up (if she doesn’t mind) and he’d take pictures of her, both soft and hard copy and straight to his hard drive.

he sees a class for the missus, the daddy AND the baby? lol who does he think is to pass out on that opportunity. he would even make them wear matching shirts and be the one in the front row to ask questions even if it isn’t time for questions yet.

harry chose the dadlife™️, but the dadlife™️ chose him too so who the fuck do the both of them think they are to not embrace one another
